        <h3>What Is Azure Functions?</h3>
        <p>
            Azure Functions is the Azure platform's version of serverless compute. This is an on-
            demand service that is configurable to be triggered by a multitude of events and capable
            of utilizing several different functional languages to execute various types of business
            logic i.e. accessing/writing to databases, reading/writing from Azure Blob storage,
            making web requests, etc.
        </p>
    </div>
